WEBVTT

00:00.000 --> 00:06.000
Your eyes deserve a spot on the diabetes checklist.

00:06.000 --> 00:13.000
Not because something's wrong — because catching things early matters.

00:13.000 --> 00:22.000
Diabetes can affect the tiny blood vessels in your eyes, sometimes before you notice any vision changes.

00:22.000 --> 00:30.000
So get a real dilated eye check — not just reading letters on a chart. The kind where they look inside the eye for early signs.

00:30.000 --> 00:42.000
Know the date of your last eye exam. Ask when the next one's due. Keep the eye doctor with your care contacts. Report blurry vision, floaters, or sudden changes right away.

00:42.000 --> 00:49.000
Small appointment. Big protection.

00:49.000 --> 00:57.000
Diabetes is a 24/7 job. You don't have to carry it alone.

00:57.000 --> 01:04.000
LocalDiabetic. We just help you carry the day. Win big.
